{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L993"},"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIControl","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"control"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"leftAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"rightAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview","title":"MLNCalloutView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNCalloutView"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclass that displays information about a selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation near that annotation."}]}}}